maftools v0.99.40
==============

Changes:
* NEW: CoOncoplot - Plot two oncoplots side by side
* NEW: rainfallPlot
* Minor changes to plotCBSsegments.

maftools v0.99.30
==============

Changes:

* NEW: Plotting and mapping variants on copy number data (require cbs segments)
* NEW: Compare two maf files for differentially mutated genes
* NEW: Forestplots
* Better clustering with copynumber and outlier detection for heterogeneity.
* Fixed bug in nmf signatures
* minor modification to titv plot

maftools v0.99.25
==============

Changes:

* inferHeterogeneity: Clustering using nonparametric dirichlet process; more plotting options.
* New subsetMaf function to subset MAF
* Upto 5X faster oncomatrix creation and sorting
* Examples won't take >5 seconds
* Fixed a warning in oncodrive function
* Updated vignette


